       conditions
       t-if:- checks the cnodition if true then only the element is rendered
       t-elif:- checks the cnodition if true then only the element is rendered
       t-else:- if t-if fails then what to do we have to give the value blank (t-else="" what to do)
       <p t-if="user.state == 'active'">User is active.</p>
       <p t-elif="user.state == 'pending'">User is pending approval.</p>
       <p t-else="">User is inactive.</p>
